<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>임준출육 이름 연구소 — 2026 이름 추천</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+KR:wght@400;500;600;700;900&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
@font-face {
  font-family: 'Binggrae';
  src: url('https://fastly.jsdelivr.net/gh/projectnoonnu/noonfonts_one@1.0/Binggrae.woff') format('woff');
  font-weight: normal;
  font-display: swap;
}
@font-face {
  font-family: 'Binggrae';
  src: url('https://fastly.jsdelivr.net/gh/projectnoonnu/noonfonts_2110@1.0/Binggrae-Bold.woff2') format('woff2');
  font-weight: 700;
  font-display: swap;
}
:root{
  --paper:#f4efe1;
  --paper-deep:#ece4cf;
  --ink:#232323;
  --ink-soft:#4a463d;
  --seal:#a83232;
  --seal-deep:#7e2424;
  --brass:#a68a52;
  --brass-soft:#cdb787;
  --line:#d8cdae;
  --card:#fbf8ef;
  --male:#2f4a63;
  --female:#a1495b;
  --neutral:#5b6b47;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box;}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
body{
  margin:0;
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at 15% 8%, rgba(168,50,50,0.04), transparent 40%),
    radial-gradient(circle at 85% 92%, rgba(166,138,82,0.06), transparent 40%),
    var(--paper);
  color:var(--ink);
  font-family:'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
  line-height:1.7;
}
::selection{background:var(--seal); color:#fff;}

/* texture */
body::before{
  content:"";
  position:fixed; inset:0; pointer-events:none; z-index:0; opacity:.5;
  background-image:
    repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.012) 0px, rgba(0,0,0,0.012) 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 3px);
}

h1,h2,h3,h4{font-family:'Noto Serif KR', serif; margin:0; color:var(--ink);}
a{color:inherit;}
p{margin:0 0 .8em;}

.layout{display:flex; max-width:1400px; margin:0 auto; position:relative; z-index:1;}

/* ---------- NAV ---------- */
.side-toggle{
  display:none;
  position:fixed; top:14px; left:14px; z-index:50;
  background:var(--seal); color:#fff; border:none; border-radius:6px;
  width:42px;height:42px; font-size:20px; cursor:pointer;
  box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.25);
}
nav.side{
  width:236px; flex:0 0 236px; position:sticky; top:0; align-self:flex-start;
  height:100vh; overflow-y:auto; padding:28px 0 40px 28px;
  border-right:1px solid var(--line);
}
nav.side .brand{
  display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; margin-bottom:26px; padding-right:16px;
}
.seal-mini{
  width:34px;height:34px; background:var(--seal); border-radius:4px; flex:0 0 auto;
  display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; color:#f4efe1;
  font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif; font-weight:900; font-size:13px; letter-spacing:-1px;
  box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,.15);
  transform:rotate(-2deg);
}
nav.side .brand-text{font-family:'Binggrae','Noto Serif KR',serif; font-weight:700; font-size:32px; line-height:1.3; color:var(--seal-deep);}
nav.side ul{list-style:none; margin:0; padding:0 16px 0 0;}
nav.side li a{
  display:block; padding:7px 10px; margin-bottom:2px; border-radius:5px;
  font-size:13.5px; color:var(--ink-soft); text-decoration:none;
  border-left:2px solid transparent;
}
nav.side li a:hover, nav.side li a.active{
  background:rgba(168,50,50,0.08); color:var(--seal-deep); border-left:2px solid var(--seal);
}
nav.side .group-label{
  font-size:11px; color:var(--brass); letter-spacing:.12em; margin:18px 0 4px 10px; font-weight:600;
}
nav.side .group-label:first-of-type{margin-top:0;}

main{flex:1; min-width:0; padding:0;}

/* ---------- HERO ---------- */
.hero{
  position:relative; padding:78px 60px 60px; overflow:hidden;
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
}
.hero::after{
  content:""; position:absolute; right:-60px; top:-60px; width:340px; height:340px;
  background:radial-gradient(circle, rgba(168,50,50,0.07), transparent 70%);
}
.hero .eyebrow{
  display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;
  font-size:12.5px; letter-spacing:.15em; color:var(--seal-deep); font-weight:600;
  margin-bottom:18px;
}
.hero .eyebrow::before{content:"卍"; opacity:0;} /* placeholder removed visually */
.hero h1{
  font-family:'Binggrae','Noto Serif KR',serif;
  font-size:clamp(34px,5vw,58px); font-weight:700; letter-spacing:-.02em; line-height:1.3;
  max-width:820px;
}
.hero h1 em{
  font-style:normal; color:var(--seal); position:relative;
}
.hero .sub{
  margin-top:22px; max-width:620px; color:var(--ink-soft); font-size:16px;
}
.hero-stamp{
  position:absolute; right:64px; top:64px; width:120px; height:120px;
  border:3px solid var(--seal); border-radius:6px; transform:rotate(-4deg);
  display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
  color:var(--seal); font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif; font-weight:900;
  font-size:22px; line-height:1.1; text-align:center; letter-spacing:2px;
  writing-mode:vertical-rl;
  background:rgba(168,50,50,0.03);
}
.hero-search{
  margin-top:32px; display:flex; gap:0; max-width:520px;
  border:1.5px solid var(--ink); border-radius:8px; overflow:hidden; background:var(--card);
}
.hero-search input{
  flex:1; border:none; background:transparent; padding:14px 16px; font-size:15px; font-family:inherit; outline:none;
}
.hero-search button{
  border:none; background:var(--ink); color:var(--paper); padding:0 22px; font-weight:600; cursor:pointer; font-size:14px;
}
.hero-search button:hover{background:var(--seal);}
.hero-note{font-size:12px; color:var(--brass); margin-top:10px;}

/* ---------- SECTIONS ---------- */
section.block{
  padding:52px 60px; border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
}
section.block:nth-of-type(even){background:rgba(236,228,207,0.35);}
.block-head{margin-bottom:30px; max-width:760px;}
.block-head .tag{
  font-size:12px; letter-spacing:.14em; color:var(--brass); font-weight:700; margin-bottom:8px; display:block;
}
.block-head h2{font-size:clamp(24px,3vw,32px); font-weight:700;}
.block-head p{color:var(--ink-soft); margin-top:10px; font-size:14.5px;}
.disclaimer{
  font-size:12px; color:var(--ink-soft); background:rgba(166,138,82,0.1); border-left:3px solid var(--brass);
  padding:8px 12px; margin-top:12px; border-radius:0 4px 4px 0; max-width:640px;
}

/* Top list grids */
.rank-grid{
  display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(150px,1fr)); gap:10px;
}
.rank-card{
  background:var(--card); border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:8px; padding:12px 14px;
  display:flex; align-items:baseline; gap:10px; transition:.15s;
}
.rank-card:hover{border-color:var(--seal); transform:translateY(-2px); box-shadow:0 6px 14px rgba(0,0,0,.06);}
.rank-card .num{font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif; font-weight:700; color:var(--brass); font-size:13px; width:22px;}
.rank-card .nm{font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif; font-weight:600; font-size:16.5px;}
.rank-card .rm{display:block; font-size:11px; color:var(--ink-soft); margin-top:1px; font-weight:400; font-family:'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif;}

.tab-row{display:flex; gap:8px; margin-bottom:20px; flex-wrap:wrap;}
.tab-btn{
  padding:8px 18px; border-radius:20px; border:1.5px solid var(--line); background:var(--card);
  cursor:pointer; font-size:13.5px; font-weight:600; color:var(--ink-soft); font-family:inherit;
}
.tab-btn.active{background:var(--ink); color:var(--paper); border-color:var(--ink);}
.tab-panel{display:none;}
.tab-panel.active{display:block;}

/* Surname section */
.surname-search{
  max-width:340px; margin-bottom:20px; padding:11px 14px; border:1.5px solid var(--line); border-radius:8px;
  font-family:inherit; font-size:14px; background:var(--card);
}
.surname-grid{
  display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(260px,1fr)); gap:14px;
}
.surname-card{
  background:var(--card); border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:10px; padding:16px 18px;
}
.surname-card .sn{
  font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif; font-weight:800; font-size:20px; color:var(--seal-deep);
  display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; margin-bottom:10px;
}
.surname-card .sn .romaja{font-size:11px; color:var(--brass); font-weight:500; font-family:'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif;}
.surname-card .picks{display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:6px;}
.chip{
  font-size:12.5px; padding:4px 10px; border-radius:14px; background:var(--paper-deep); color:var(--ink);
  font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif; font-weight:500;
}
.chip.m{border:1px solid rgba(47,74,99,.35); color:var(--male);}
.chip.f{border:1px solid rgba(161,73,91,.35); color:var(--female);}
.chip.n{border:1px solid rgba(91,107,71,.35); color:var(--neutral);}

/* hanja table */
.hanja-grid{
  display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(220px,1fr)); gap:10px;
}
.hanja-card{
  background:var(--card); border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:8px; padding:12px 14px; display:flex; gap:12px; align-items:center;
}
.hanja-card .hz{
  font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif; font-size:30px; font-weight:700; color:var(--ink); width:42px; text-align:center; flex:none;
}
.hanja-card .hz-info b{font-size:14px; display:block;}
.hanja-card .hz-info span{font-size:12px; color:var(--ink-soft);}
.hanja-card .badge{
  font-size:10px; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:8px; margin-left:6px; font-family:'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif;
}
.badge.m{background:rgba(47,74,99,.12); color:var(--male);}
.badge.f{background:rgba(161,73,91,.12); color:var(--female);}
.badge.n{background:rgba(91,107,71,.12); color:var(--neutral);}

/* simple pill lists */
.pill-list{display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px;}
.pill{
  background:var(--card); border:1px solid var(--line); padding:8px 15px; border-radius:20px;
  font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif; font-size:14.5px; font-weight:600;
}
.pill small{display:block; font-family:'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif; font-weight:400; font-size:10.5px; color:var(--ink-soft); margin-top:1px;}

/* generator */
.gen-toolbar{
  display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:10px; align-items:center; margin-bottom:18px;
}
.gen-toolbar select, .gen-toolbar input{
  padding:9px 12px; border-radius:7px; border:1.5px solid var(--line); font-family:inherit; font-size:13.5px; background:var(--card);
}
.gen-toolbar button{
  padding:9px 18px; border-radius:7px; border:none; background:var(--seal); color:#fff; font-weight:700; cursor:pointer; font-size:13.5px;
}
.gen-toolbar button:hover{background:var(--seal-deep);}
.gen-count{font-size:12.5px; color:var(--brass); font-weight:700; margin-left:auto;}
.gen-grid{
  display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(140px,1fr)); gap:8px;
  max-height:520px; overflow-y:auto; padding:4px; border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:10px; background:rgba(255,255,255,.35);
}
.gen-item{
  background:var(--card); border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:7px; padding:9px 11px; text-align:center;
}
.gen-item .kn{font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif; font-weight:700; font-size:15px;}
.gen-item .en{font-size:10.5px; color:var(--ink-soft); margin-top:2px;}

/* tips */
.tip-cards{display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(260px,1fr)); gap:16px;}
.tip-card{
  background:var(--card); border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:10px; padding:20px;
  border-top:3px solid var(--seal);
}
.tip-card h4{font-size:15.5px; margin-bottom:8px;}
.tip-card p{font-size:13.5px; color:var(--ink-soft); margin:0;}

/* romanization table */
.roman-table{width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; font-size:13px;}
.roman-table th,.roman-table td{padding:8px 10px; border-bottom:1px solid var(--line); text-align:left;}
.roman-table th{color:var(--brass); font-weight:700; font-size:11.5px; letter-spacing:.06em;}
.roman-try{
  display:flex; gap:10px; margin:18px 0 26px; max-width:420px;
}
.roman-try input{flex:1; padding:11px 14px; border:1.5px solid var(--line); border-radius:8px; font-family:inherit; font-size:14px;}
.roman-try button{padding:0 20px; border-radius:8px; border:none; background:var(--ink); color:var(--paper); font-weight:700; cursor:pointer;}
.roman-result{
  margin-top:10px; font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif; font-size:20px; min-height:28px; color:var(--seal-deep);
}

/* footer */
footer{
  padding:60px 60px 40px; text-align:center; background:var(--paper-deep);
}
footer .divider{
  width:60px; height:2px; background:var(--brass); margin:0 auto 30px;
}
.kakao-btn{
  display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; padding:16px 34px;
  background:var(--seal); color:#fff; border-radius:30px; text-decoration:none;
  font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif; font-weight:700; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:.02em;
  box-shadow:0 8px 20px rgba(168,50,50,.25); transition:.15s;
}
.kakao-btn:hover{background:var(--seal-deep); transform:translateY(-2px);}
footer .copyright{margin-top:26px; font-size:12px; color:var(--ink-soft); letter-spacing:.02em;}
footer .copyright b{color:var(--ink); font-family:'Noto Serif KR',serif;}

@media (max-width:900px){
  nav.side{position:fixed; left:0; top:0; z-index:40; background:var(--paper); transform:translateX(-100%); transition:.25s; box-shadow:0 0 30px rgba(0,0,0,.15);}
  nav.side.open{transform:translateX(0);}
  .side-toggle{display:block;}
  .hero, section.block{padding:60px 22px 44px;}
  .hero{padding-top:90px;}
  .hero-stamp{display:none;}
  footer{padding:50px 20px 34px;}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<button class="side-toggle" id="navToggle">☰</button>

<div class="layout">
<nav class="side" id="sideNav">
  <div class="brand">
    <div class="brand-text">임준출육</div>
  </div>
  <span class="group-label">인기 순위</span>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="#top-male">2026 인기 남자 이름</a></li>
    <li><a href="#top-female">2026 인기 여자 이름</a></li>
    <li><a href="#top-neutral">2026 인기 중성 이름</a></li>
  </ul>
  <span class="group-label">성씨 · 유형별</span>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="#by-surname">성씨별 추천</a></li>
    <li><a href="#pure-korean">순우리말 이름</a></li>
    <li><a href="#one-syllable">한 글자 이름</a></li>
    <li><a href="#two-syllable">두 글자 이름</a></li>
    <li><a href="#rare-names">희귀한 이름</a></li>
  </ul>
  <span class="group-label">한자</span>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="#hanja-table">이름용 한자 · 뜻</a></li>
  </ul>
  <span class="group-label">대량 추천</span>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="#gen-male">남자 이름 500+</a></li>
    <li><a href="#gen-female">여자 이름 500+</a></li>
    <li><a href="#gen-neutral">중성 이름 300+</a></li>
    <li><a href="#unisex">성별 무관 이름</a></li>
  </ul>
  <span class="group-label">가이드</span>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="#tips">이름 조합 팁</a></li>
    <li><a href="#romanization">영문 표기</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<main>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <div class="hero">
    <span class="eyebrow">2026 NAMING GUIDE · 임준출육</span>
    <h1>태어날 아이에게<br>줄 수 있는 첫 <em>선물</em>,<br>이름을 함께 짓습니다</h1>
    <p class="sub">성씨와 궁합이 좋은 이름, 순우리말 이름, 이름에 쓰기 좋은 한자와 그 뜻, 그리고 2026년 인기 이름까지 — 남자·여자·중성 이름 1,300개 이상을 한 곳에서 찾아보세요.</p>
    <div class="hero-search">
      <input id="heroSearch" type="text" placeholder="성씨나 원하는 느낌의 글자를 입력해보세요 (예: 김, 서)">
      <button onclick="document.getElementById('by-surname').scrollIntoView()">성씨로 찾기</button>
    </div>
    <p class="hero-note">※ 본 사이트의 인기 순위는 최근 출생신고 경향과 작명 트렌드를 참고해 구성한 예상 리스트이며, 통계청 등 공식 통계와 정확히 일치하지 않을 수 있습니다.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- TOP MALE -->
  <section class="block" id="top-male">
    <div class="block-head">
      <span class="tag">RANKING · BOYS</span>
      <h2>2026 인기 남자 이름 TOP 50</h2>
      <p>부드러운 발음과 트렌디한 한자 조합이 강세인 해입니다. 온화하면서도 힘있는 어감의 이름이 상위권을 차지했습니다.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rank-grid" id="topMaleGrid"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- TOP FEMALE -->
  <section class="block" id="top-female">
    <div class="block-head">
      <span class="tag">RANKING · GIRLS</span>
      <h2>2026 인기 여자 이름 TOP 50</h2>
      <p>맑고 청량한 어감과 순우리말이 섞인 이름, 짧고 세련된 두 글자 이름이 인기를 이끌고 있습니다.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rank-grid" id="topFemaleGrid"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- TOP NEUTRAL -->
  <section class="block" id="top-neutral">
    <div class="block-head">
      <span class="tag">RANKING · UNISEX</span>
      <h2>2026 인기 중성 이름 TOP 30</h2>
      <p>성별을 특정하지 않는 담백한 이름을 선호하는 부모님이 늘면서 중성 이름의 비중이 꾸준히 상승 중입니다.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rank-grid" id="topNeutralGrid"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- SURNAME -->
  <section class="block" id="by-surname">
    <div class="block-head">
      <span class="tag">BY SURNAME</span>
      <h2>성씨별 추천 이름</h2>
      <p>성씨의 음운(받침·모음)과 어울리는 이름을 골랐습니다. 받침이 있는 성씨는 모음으로 시작하는 이름이, 받침이 없는 성씨는 리듬감 있는 이름이 잘 어울립니다.</p>
    </div>
    <input class="surname-search" id="surnameSearch" placeholder="성씨 검색 (예: 김, 이, 박...)">
    <div class="surname-grid" id="surnameGrid"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- PURE KOREAN -->
  <section class="block" id="pure-korean">
    <div class="block-head">
      <span class="tag">PURE KOREAN</span>
      <h2>순우리말 이름</h2>
      <p>한자 없이 그 자체로 뜻을 지니는 고유어 이름입니다. 이름에 담긴 뜻을 함께 표기했습니다.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="tab-row">
      <button class="tab-btn active" data-tab="pk-m">남자</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="pk-f">여자</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="pk-n">중성</button>
    </div>
    <div id="pk-m" class="tab-panel active"><div class="pill-list" id="pkMaleList"></div></div>
    <div id="pk-f" class="tab-panel"><div class="pill-list" id="pkFemaleList"></div></div>
    <div id="pk-n" class="tab-panel"><div class="pill-list" id="pkNeutralList"></div></div>
  </section>

  <!-- ONE SYLLABLE -->
  <section class="block" id="one-syllable">
    <div class="block-head">
      <span class="tag">MONOSYLLABIC</span>
      <h2>한 글자 이름</h2>
      <p>깔끔하고 힘있는 어감의 외자 이름. 부르기 쉽고 영문 표기도 간결합니다.</p>
